ETa - Epcis Trusted Agent

Agent of access control for the EPCIS.

Dependencies:
  IoTa modules:
    - LibXACML-EPCIS
    - EPCIS-Xi-Client
    - Mu
  libraries:
    - epcis-commons
    - epcis-repository
    - epcis-queryclient
    - epcis-captureclient
    - spring
    - cxf
    - servlet-api
    - commons-logging
    - log4j

Installation and Configuration:
  IoTa-Installer installs and configures ETa.
  (application.properties for this application,
   commons-logging.properties and log4j.properties for the logs)
  Use the script ldap.sh in IoTa-Installer/lib (root privileges required) to
   configure the LDAP directory.
  Modify the tomcat-users.xml file of Tomcat to manage identity
   with TLS. See the INSTALL file.

Usage Dependencies:
  - a MySQL server
  - an Epcis
  - EpcisPHI
  - a DWS
  - EpcILoN
  - an ONS

Usage:
  like an Epcis
